<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><colour id="3" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然然<colour id="65535" />帶來的花卉種子還有灌木樹苗，<delay20 />
都是<colour id="1" />Nook商店<colour id="65535" />裡沒有販售的東西喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且商品品質也是一流，<delay20 />在那傢伙的店裡
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總是會一不小心就買太多呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">灌木這種植物，<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />根據種類不同
開花的季節也不一樣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />根據季節思考要種植怎樣的灌木，<delay20 />
也是一件很有趣的事喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次要種哪個好呢～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到花草樹木時，<delay20 />總能感到些許的放鬆呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果地球日能讓更多人喜歡上植物的話，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會感到很開心的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我來教你<tag a="110" b="10" />流派的園藝技巧吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其訣竅就是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />靠著氣勢和直覺，<delay8 />種滿自己喜歡的花卉！<delay frames="30" />
完畢！<delay frames="40" /><delay20 /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說完全無法當作參考嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當我覺得該為島上環境貢獻心力而開始
拔雜草時，<delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><colour id="3" />然然<colour id="65535" />那傢伙竟然<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「難道，<delay20 />你是雜草之神的使者嗎～？」<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對著我說這種話喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙<delay20 />有時候還真是奇妙呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
